name: faith silk
description: "faith silk"– is made of maps of india, thailand, saudi arabia, chad and sudan. it's a classic cut with a unique flowing line that celebrates the power of feminine beauty. the fabric treatment is to sew sheer crinkle silk onto soft thin white cotton. there are multi-color prints on turquoise blue silk chiffon. this silk article is hand-printed and handmade, so please hand wash only.
